agent_kg is a knowledge graph mcp server to provide a "memento" class of AI agents with
 - episodic memory
 - factual memory
 - task planning and result history

It is implemented as a postgresql database application.

While the primary tables implement an ERP / knowledge graph, 
it contains specialized tables for "system" information, such as
initialization instructions.

The schema is described in schema.sq

Other design information is in .design